name: SloganMachine

”give me a slogan”

skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: slogan machine
des: Ask Alexa to read you a slogan and she'll tell you a random slogan for a random thing. Slogans are for everyday things. If you have a thing you want Henry to write a slogan for, send him a tweet at @tehawesome on Twitter.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
